    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>With soothing song or tales, you lull the target into an enchanting dream. When you cast the spell, the target falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} if it wasn't already. While @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious}, it experiences a dream of your choice. If it sleeps for at least 1 minute, it gains the benefit of the dream for the remainder of the spell's duration.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dream of Insight</strong> +1 status bonus to Intelligence-based skill checks</li>\n<li><strong>Dream of Glamour</strong> +1 status bonus to Charisma-based skill checks</li>\n<li><strong>Dream of Voyaging</strong> +5-foot status bonus to Speed If you Cast this Spell again, the effects of any previous sweet dream you cast end.</li>\n</ul>",
